BOOTSTRAP is a CSS framework
this framework contains pre written codes for various tasks
this make our css coding much easier

DISADVANTAGES->we cant have full control over our website css if we use this framework,grid and flexbox are better in this scenario

WHEN TO USE->when we need to build a responsive website quickly which works on mobile as well as desktop

LINKS TO GET BOOTSTRAP

MAIN LINK->just below <head>

<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM" crossorigin="anonymous"

SECOND LINK->just above </body>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-geWF76RCwLtnZ8qwWowPQNguL3RmwHVBC9FhGdlKrxdiJJigb/j/68SIy3Te4Bkz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
